Package com.example.inventorymanager

Class ItemTest

java.lang.Object
com.example.inventorymanager.ItemTest
public class ItemTest extends Object
Tests the functionality of the Item() class. Ensures that all getters and setters work properly and that the item can be properly transformed into a database document.
Author:
Isaac Joffe
